shortDescription: Commander, we've just received a distress signal from one of our facilities on the planet. Xenomorphs have overun the entire facility, and subverted the base's defense systems. Satellite imagery tells us they're preparing for an assault on the secondary base. We need a rapid response force to eliminate their Invasion, and level the seized base. Our own forces are inbound but won't get there in time to save the secondary base.
longDescription: We've got to intercept 'Mechs, destroy a base, save a base... and there are base defense systems? Sounds like a mess.And possibly a horror movie.

dialogueContent.words: *****STATIC*** Thi**** Ahhh*** NO!****.
Well, looks like another day of weirdness Commander. Hope We can end this nightmare soon.
Looks Like they are crawling around everywhere. We will have to Intercept this group if we are going to have a chance.
The Defensive Turrets are at least online. Hope they are packing the flame varients.
We got to take out their nest to have any chance though.
I'll be ready at a moments notice to get out of their.
We survived? Thank You Argo!
Let's pack it up, folks. Commander, we'll debrief back in orbit.
I recomend orbital nukes at this point commander.
There's those base defenses, Commander. Looks like the turrets are reacting to the IFF signatures of the infected mechs and powering up.
Commander, I'm seeing hostile defenders surrounding the enemy base.
We can't complete the contract until those units are destroyed.
Commander, they've got infected units spread out around the target facility. If we clean them out, our employers won't have to; they're offering a bonus. It's your call.
That's the first target structure down, Commander. Keep up the pressure.
Argo, They are invading our strong hold, they are so Slimy!
Argo, we will pray for our lost souls,but you ahve to be faster or we'll lose them all!
Argo, we're under heavy-- [static]-- hold out-- [static]
Dammit! [Static] [Sounds of gunshots] We cannot hold!
Boom! Good kill, boss!
Meyer, cut the chatter and get ready for the pickup.
Commander, we've completed all the primary objectives and you're clear to extract.
I'm on station to pick you up here whenever you're ready, boss.
As long as you're still in the AO, Commander, you'll need to keep the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base secure.
Uh, Commander, I'm not seeing any more blips out there. I think you killed everything.
Well, that's one way to protect a facility. Commander, there's a {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} lance ready to relieve you.
When you're ready to extract, Sumire will pick you up at this location.
Heads up, commander, a lance of  Xenomorphic units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
We'll have to destroy that lance if we want to complete the mission.
Heads up, commander, a lance of Xenomorphic units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
If we destroy them we'll get a hefty bonus.
Commander, I'm seeing hostile Xenomorphic units in the area. Must be two queens here.
Our employer is saying we NEED to kill those units. Prepare to engage.
Commander, I'm seeing hostile Xenomorphic units in the area.
If we decide to kill these units our employer if offering a bonus.
Incoming Xenomorphic Droppods!
Our employer wants us to kill these guys. This mission isn't ending until they die.
Incoming Xenomorphic dropship!
Our employer is offering us some extra cash if we destroy these units too.
Scratch another target.
Good job, commander. All primary objectives complete. Get to evac, Sumire will pick you up here.
Shit. Commander, a Xenomorphic infected dropship just set down. Looks like they have more
They seem fairly determined to hold this facility. We need to hurry before even more of them show up.
Boss, that's another Xenomorph lance in the field. Getting kinda crowded down there.
Well, the good news is that I don't see any more inbound DropShips... the bad news is that's another enemy lance.
Watch out commander, more hostiles are arriving. They'll be landing in this area.
Watch out commander, more hostiles are arriving. They'll be landing in this area.
Commander, we've got a lance of enemy forces moving towards the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base.
They're coming in fast, don't let them get too close.
Commander, we've got a lance of enemy forces moving towards the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base.
They're coming in fast, don't let them get too close.
Commander, Xenomorphic reinforcements are inbound to this location.
Commander, Xenomorphic reinforcements are inbound to this location.
Commander, Xenomorphic reinforcements are inbound to this location.
The {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Name} has provided some of their own forces to support us.
They're here to defend their base and will engage any hostiles that get too close.
Commander, the employer's base is under attack! Our {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} allies will stay close to the base to defend it.
